org.friendlysnmp.event

Interface FTableSetListener


  • public interface FTableSetListener
    Implement this interface and register it with FTable object to receive SET events from MIB browser.
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.8 $
    See Also:
    FTable

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void set(FTable table, FID idRow, FColumn col, TableRowAction action)
      Register object of this class with FTable and this method will be called on SET event from MIB browser.

      • set

        void set(FTable table,
       FID idRow,
       FColumn col,
       TableRowAction action)
        Register object of this class with FTable and this method will be called on SET event from MIB browser.
        Parameters:
        table - MIB table changed by MIB browser
        idRow - changed row ID
        col - column
        action - one of CHANGE, DELETE, CREATE
